name: Schrödinger's Experiment
description: This piece is visualization of Schrodinger's imaginary experiment in interactive Heliantone style, where the sound of Geiger Counter superposes the cat over Schrodinger's portrait. When observed cat exists in both states[alive/not alive] even Schrodinger's himself . Click/Tap to interact / repeat the experiment | @atimtay | https://linktr.ee/atimtakus
